text: Agar tujhe lagta hai mai tera memoir likhunga to aisa nhi hai. Hum to sath me kahani likhte rahenge bal safed hone tak.
author: Archit  Mishra

text: Seedhi si bat hai, agar poori kahaniyan likhne lag gye to bechare doosre logon ke panno pe kabja karna padega is book me. Har ek kand to tere sath hi kiya hai. Tere bare me tere sa jada to mujhe pta hoga. Kab kis class me kispe dil aya, konse gane sunke heartbreak sambhala, wo 8th class wali ab kahan hai, kis principal ki beti......khair chhodiyeüòÇ. Tera Past, Present Future, sabka pta hai mujhe. 4 saal me zada nhi to 2-3 hajar movies dekh ae honge hum. Apna yarana aisa ki mai teri kanghi use karta aur tu meri, mai tera deo aur tu mera. Dil itna bada is ladke ka ki bhale hi 200 degree bukhar kyo na ho, dosto ko kabhi mana nhi karega. Aur itna openhearted, ki dosti yaari ke samne kuch aur nhi dikhta. Bharat sarkar se zada loan maaf to apne Saini ne kiye honge! Jab bhi kisi form me pucha jata ki Contact person dalo IITK me, to bina soche tera hi naam likh jata. Wo kahaniya yad kar karke neend ab bhi ud jati hai. Haan bas gala kuch zada nasaz rehta hai iska. Sath me itne patake phode ki Green diwali me dhuan dhuan ho gaya. Mere ghar to itni bar aya ki rasta hi yaad ho gya. Ab ana to mujhe hai, shaitan Tubby se milne!!  Lekin ek bat hai, kabhi isse movie decide karne ko mat kahiyega bhul se bhi. A friend to treasure for a Lifetime‚ù§!!
author: Archit  Mishra

text: To me, you're the "Thinks more speaks less" guy. Never seen you nonsensing around. Vrindavan trip yaad hai? Kata tha apna lekin maze kiye the. Baithe baithe pair so jate the aur Prem mandir hi nhi leke gye bc. Tu aya tha to kaju tha. All the best for your future bro!
author: Archit  Mishra

text: Sir! Classes me tu na bolta to poora sannata chhaya rehta. Bhale hi tu RR karta tha courses me lekin I guess tu hi aisa banda hai jo end me "kya seekha" pe zada dhyan feta hai instead of "kitne number aye"! And you acknowledge your own mistakes, which is something very few do. Respect for that! Tabhi to tujhe mai Sir bulata hoon ^_^ TA project me kafi metal katwaya tumse. Btw cute hai tu. Agar insaan nhi hota to pakka bhalu hota!
author: Archit  Mishra

text: Tu insan nhi powerhouse hai. PE ground me no stop 10 chakkar, 5 km race me jaha baki sab halfway tapak gye waha ye ladka usain bolt ke speed se bhag ke 2nd aya tha. Hockey me tera jalwa dekh kar fanmoments aane lagte the mujheüòÇ. Kafi masti kari humne sath me. Summer ki garmi me 3 km Bun makhan khane jana, raat ke 1 baje Hall 4 canteen me team ko gariyana aur bhot kuch! Bhot genuine aur soft spoken person hai tu bhai. Milte rahenge.
author: Archit  Mishra

text:
Sala naam hi chura liya. Tu reporting wale din merejust age tha, fir usne naam bulaya Archit, fir hall jake pata laga tu bhai hai . Teri vishudh harami se lekar satwik purush tak ki journey ko bhot closely dekha hai. You are a testimony ki bc agarkoi chicken lover non veg chhod sakta hai, to insan kuch bhi kar sakta hai. Bas resolve tagda hona chahiye. All the best! 
(Bach ke rehna teri chequebook mere hath lag gyi to dikkat me a jaoge)
author: Archit  Mishra

text: Kayanat hai tu. Chemical ka only non virgin banda. Wo kissa poora sunna hai mujhe. NCL me raat raat padhai karte the yaad hai. All the best for the future bro! Keep in touch
author: Archit  Mishra

text: Bhaiya me bhaiya Mishra bhaiya! Panditon ki shan (inke khud ke according), satvik achar vichar wala launda. Lekin agar iske door ke handle me sutli bomb lagado to  jaan ke peeche pad jaega. Handle with Care material hai sala. Kabhi bhi fuse ud sakta hai, aur ud gaya to bawal kar deta hai. Akhri ke ek mahine me kya masti kari poore ek sal ka compensate kar diya. 2  baje CESE wala fountain bhi chalenge pakka. Ya OAT ki stairs pe "bas mujhe shanti se baithne do yahan" wo bhi karwaenge. Mere waste hone ke baad tune kandhe pe leke room tak chhoda tha, will always remember. You know what else I'll always remember, ganje ke baad wala tera wo chehraüòÇ. (Is vishay me bhot kuch likh sakta hun....huehuehue)! Milte rehna bsdk. bros before hoes.
author: Archit  Mishra

text: DUGC ka dahina hath, Hon'ble President Shree Kreenight! Department ko HOD se achha koi samajhta hai to wo tu hai. Aur  Techkriti PUBG championship me mujhe nade se udane ke liye maaf nhi karunga....xdxd.
author: Archit  Mishra

text: Are Mannu Tonk wale, Bhai hai tu bhai! Sabse sweet, caring aur wholesome banda. 4 saal me jada nhi to 4 lac bar tujhe moti gand bulaya hoga sabne lekin kabhi mind nhi kiya(ab jo sach hai wo sach hai). Aur 400 baar "Kal se canteen band" bhi kiya hoga tune. Mujhe personal recommendation dene ka shukriya. Kafi maze kiye hamne SAE me. Ek bat to hai, gajab ka dedication hai tujhme. Jis kam ki thaan li use poora karke hi manta hai. btw wo bolte hain  "Jo tera hai wo mera hai", apne liye hi bana hai. Meri room ka adha saman tere pas ar tera mere pas. Kuch cheeze clear karna chahta hu - "Kachodi usi ko kehte hain", SMEX milna mushkil hai", "JTG ka matlab Jitesh the Gandu hai" aur "Tu bhai hai". Thank you for making my stay of 4 years so memorable!!
author: Archit  Mishra

text: PM, aka GOD. Ye wo ladka hai jo kranti la sakta hai desh me. I'll be waiting for the day when you overthrow the govt and call me to offer a job in Waffen-SS (achha waffen thoda zyada hogya). text: Ragmah, chalta phirta encyclopedia. Nhi mujhe batao, koi aisa insan dekha hai jo khade khade bata de Sri Lanka me konsi language kitne percent log bolte hain? Ya fir 10 countries ki GDP? I'll say once again, agar KBC me gaya to phone a friend me tera hi number doonga. Gym partner, jiska har day leg day hota hai. Agli bar jab mile to 10 pack abs hone chahiye. Peene ke bad aisi chadhti hai ki bhul jata hai insan hai ya kutta, aur tera slow motion mode...xdxd. Yar itna awesome kaise hai tu! Milte rahenge Bangalore me apan.

text: Thisss guy right here, he is not a guy, he is a cocktail of 10 kilo brains, 50 kilo talent, 50 kilo mehnat, and everything one can imagine to make the perfectest human possible. Jis field ko utha lo usme chaap deta hai, Volley, Swimming, Baddy, Football, Classical, bc tu khata kya hai?? Pehle month me hi mai jaan gaya ki ye ladka aag lagadega! Humne kafi maze kiye last ke month me and I got to know you better as a person! Its hard to pick a single domain jahan tu perfect nhi hai. Singapore aunga fir Sea side wali road pe Vodka bhi peeni hai(aur wo top floor se jump bhi). Ghar ate rehna. btw Request accept nhi hui !_!

text: Ath Sachin. Wing ka giraffe, Daande, Lambu, Hagga, Jumper, kya nhi hai tu! Pyara insan hai tu. Hamesha hasta rehta. Ba thali me khana chhod deta hai kabhi kabhi.
